targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
SELECT
   
    quantile(0.99)(average_time) as "99",
    quantile(0.95)(average_time) as "95",
    quantile(0.90)(average_time) as "90",
     quantile(0.80)(average_time) as "80",
     quantile(0.70)(average_time) as "70",
      quantile(0.60)(average_time) as "60",
       quantile(0.50)(average_time) as "50",
        quantile(0.40)(average_time) as "40",
         quantile(0.30)(average_time) as "30",
          quantile(0.20)(average_time) as "20",
           quantile(0.10)(average_time) as "10"
FROM jmresults_statistic js
WHERE
    profile_name = '$LEFT_PROFILE'
    and run_id = '$LEFT_RUN' and res_code='200' and sample_label in ($LEFT_SAMPLE) 
GROUP BY
    
    sample_label
ORDER BY
    
    sample_label

targets.formattedQuery: SELECT percentile("responseTime", 90) FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE  "testName" =~ /^$profile$/ AND "runId" =~ /^$runid$/ AND "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
targets.query:
WITH
    (select min(timestamp_sec) from jmresults_statistic where profile_name = '$LEFT_PROFILE' and run_id = '$LEFT_RUN') as left_test,
    (select min(timestamp_sec) from jmresults_statistic where profile_name = '$RIGHT_PROFILE' and run_id = '$RIGHT_RUN') as right_test
    SELECT (intDiv(toUInt32(timestamp_sec-(right_test - left_test)), $agr) * $agr) * 1000  as t,
    quantile(0.95)(average_time) as "97perc",
    sample_label|| '_RIGHT'  as "sample_label"
FROM jmresults_statistic js
WHERE
    profile_name = '$RIGHT_PROFILE'
    and run_id = '$RIGHT_RUN' and res_code='200'
GROUP BY
    t,
    sample_label
ORDER BY 
    t,sample_label
